Hello and welcome to the storymode of Nitro Racing! My nameis Tom and I'll be your coach  throughout your racing career
Before you start racing, let's start with a bit of training!  Here's a kart for you. You canpratice the controls on this   practice track
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish the pratice track
Now that you are warmed up, how about you start racing!   There's currently a kart race  going on here in California.
The other racers at this event are experienced kart racers,   but I'm sure that you have thetalent to do well on the track.
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 5
Congrats on your last race! Youdid really good! In fact you didso well that car racers in     Canada invited you for a race.
A Mini Cooper will be the     perfect car for this race. Its great handling will be ideal forthis curvy track.
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 4
Good job on your last race!    For the next one, I have a     special suprise for you that   you'll need for the next event
But... you'll need to earn thissuprise by completing my fun  challenge! The challenge I give you is to find every fountain  in New York city!
There are 5 of them.               Good luck!!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Find the 5 fountains
You completed my challenge in no time! As promised, here is my suprise: A 1970 Dodge      Charger
You are going to need this car for your next race as we are  going to a muscle car event in Nevada.
Muscle cars are fast but they do not have the best handling  so make sure to use the brake before each turn.
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 3
One of the racers you defeatedlast race is not so happy aboutit. His name is Rick and he    wants revenge.
He challenges you to race      against him. The first one to  arrive at Las Vegas wins the   race. Show him what you're  made of!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish the race first
Good job beating Rick at the   last race! A lot of people in   the area heard that you won   and are starting to realize howtalented you are!
Before we go to Japan for yournext event, a special fan yours,Jack,who has a cool car      collection,wants to give you a special gift.
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Find Jack's house in Vegas
I can't believe that Jack gave you his Toyota ae86 as a gift! The toyota ae86 will be perfectfor the future drifing event inJapan.
Before we go to Japan, let's  practice your drifting skills. Iprepared this pratice drift    track. It's the perfect place  to learn drifting!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Complete the pratice track
Welcome to Japan! The next   event is a drift competition   where each driver must       complete the course as fast aspossible.
You'll be using the same Toyotaae86 which is going to be      perfect for this track's sharp turns!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in less than 3min
Welcome to Tokyo! The race   takes place directly in the     streets of the city and only   japanese cars are allowed for this race.
For this race, you'll be using  the Toyota Supra. This car is  super fast, so make sure you  do not go too fast before eachturn. Good luck!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 2
The next race is held in       Australia! Racers will be very fast as this is an internationalevent where only experienced  drivers are allowed.
There will be a total of 12    drivers this time and you'll bedriving the same Supra you    used in Japan. Good luck!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 4
Congrats on your last race!    People arround the globe are   starting to notice you!
You've been invited to a very  special event in Autralia whereeach drivers races buses... yesbuses! I can't wait to see how good of a bus driver you are!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 3
Welcome back to Canada for   the second time this year,but this time, as you can see,it's a lot colder!
For this event, you'll need to go as fast as possible and set the fasted time to win. But  watch out! A part of the trackis covered with snow!
This is why you'll be using theFord Bronco which is perfect  for off-road driving!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in less than 1:45 min
We're back to the US  and thistime in Northern California foran electric vehicle race!
Electric cars are very quick,  so be prepared for a fast     acceleration! You'll be driving a Tesla model 3 against other  expert racers.
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 2
You did absolutely amazing thisyear! In fact, you did so well that you were invited to one  of the most important cham- pionships: The Nitro Racing     Championship!
The Nitro Racing Championship  is your final event this season.It is devided in 3 races, each  with different cars. To take  part in the first race,you needto qualify.
The first race is with sport   road cars. You'll be driving a  Mustang. Make sure you do notgo to fast in each turn and    good luck!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 5
Congrats on your last race! Youqualified for the second event!In the next event, you'll be   racing on a NASCAR race track.
This track is oval, so you'll   only need to turn right. Other racers are also talented so be prepared for a high-speed race!
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 5
Good job on the NASCAR track! You qualified for the supercar event where each racers will  be driving multi-million dollar cars. Exciting right?
You'll be driving a Lamborghini Huracan.This cars is extremely quick so make sure you do not go too fast into each corner   at first.
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 5
You have reached the Nitro     Racing Championship finals. Forthe final race, everyone is    driving in Formula 1 cars.
F1 cars have the best handling,so be prepared for an intense  race! If you finish this race   first, I get you a new unique  car. Deal?
Objective to clear the mission:                              - Finish in the Top 1
